{"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"platforms":["iOS"],"tokens":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"@property"},{"kind":"text","text":" ("},{"kind":"keyword","text":"nonatomic"},{"kind":"text","text":", "},{"kind":"keyword","text":"assign"},{"kind":"text","text":") "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"BOOL","preciseIdentifier":"c:@T@BOOL"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"showsUserLocation"},{"kind":"text","text":";"}],"languages":["occ"]}]},{"kind":"content","content":[{"text":"Discussion","anchor":"discussion","level":2,"type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Setting this property to "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"YES"},{"type":"text","text":" causes the map view to use the Core Location"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"framework to find the current location. As long as this property is "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"YES"},{"type":"text","text":", the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"map view continues to track the user’s location and update it periodically."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"This property does not indicate whether the user’s position is actually visible"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"on the map, only whether the map view is allowed to display it. To determine"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"whether the user’s position is visible, use the "},{"code":"userLocationVisible","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" property."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"The default value of this property is "},{"code":"NO","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":"."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Your app must specify a value for ","type":"text"},{"code":"NSLocationWhenInUseUsageDescription","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" or","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"code":"NSLocationAlwaysUsageDescription","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" in its ","type":"text"},{"code":"Info.plist","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" to satisfy the","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"requirements of the underlying Core Location framework when enabling this","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"property.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"If you implement a custom location manager, set the "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"locationManager"},{"type":"text","text":" before"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"calling "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"showsUserLocation"},{"type":"text","text":"."}],"type":"paragraph"}]}],"kind":"symbol","hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre","doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapView"]]},"sections":[],"metadata":{"remoteSource":{"fileName":"MLNMapView.h","url":"https:\/\/github.com\/maplibre\/maplibre-native\/blob\/main\/platform\/ios\/src\/MLNMapView.h#L590"},"role":"symbol","roleHeading":"Instance Property","symbolKind":"property","fragments":[{"text":"showsUserLocation","kind":"identifier"}],"externalID":"c:objc(cs)MLNMapView(py)showsUserLocation","title":"showsUserLocation","navigatorTitle":[{"text":"showsUserLocation","kind":"identifier"}],"modules":[{"name":"MapLibre"}]},"schemaVersion":{"minor":3,"major":0,"patch":0},"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapView\/showsUserLocation","interfaceLanguage":"occ"},"abstract":[{"text":"A Boolean value indicating whether the map may display the user location.","type":"text"}],"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnmapview\/showsuserlocation"]}],"references":{"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNMapView":{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapView","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnmapview","title":"MLNMapView","role":"symbol","type":"topic","fragments":[{"kind":"identifier